-- General Growth Properties to Sell $1.3 Billion of Bonds in Revised Plan
-- Victoria Batchelor
-- 2010-08-03T03:21:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-08-03/general-growth-properties-to-sell-1-3-billion-of-bonds-in-revised-plan.html

          
          
             General Growth Properties Inc. said
it has filed an amended Plan of Reorganization, Disclosure
Statement and amended Investment Agreements with the United
States Bankruptcy Court for the Southern District of New York.  
          
          


  


        